c: 11
v: 84
t: "And (to the people of) Midian (We sent as Messenger) their brother Shu‘ayb. He said (conveying the same message): \"O my people! Worship God: you have no deity other than Him. Do not give short measure and weight (in your dealings). Surely I see you affluent (in wealth which you have gained in unlawful ways), and I fear for you the punishment of an all-encompassing Day"